About
Be whisked away by Cirque Du Soleil’s 'O', an aquatic and acrobatic extravaganza at the Bellagio in Las Vegas. This surreal and theatrical show features acrobats, synchronized swimmers and divers performing emotive and death-defying acts in the water and on floating rafts, suspended steel ships, and 60-foot platforms. The first few rows are the designated splash zone, so you might want to bring a waterproof jacket if you want to stay dry. Get a regular ticket, or treat yourself to the V.I.P. Experience, which includes suite seats, an exclusive meet and greet, champagne, and a guided tour. – Tripadvisor

I pilastri sono posizionati strategicamente in linea con le uscite di sicurezza per ridurre al minimo le ostruzioni per il pubblico.
